name: Advertising experiment #8
description: This is an advertising experiment. Owners of this OBJKT will be listed as "featured user" on the exploration tool <https://projects.stroep.nl/hicetnunc/> until 14/06/2021. On each page view the featured user is randomly chosen. The data will be fetched using the API from <https://better-call.dev>, so once collected the collector should be featured directly. If you collect more, you get featured more often, but it's also possible to sell it on secondary market during the week or give to friends! Who owns it, gets featured.
